say | wolf | Congratulations and welcome to Tallinn University!
say | wolf | Being new to Tallinn can be a whirlwind, so I'll guide you through your necessary documents while you enjoy exploring the city.
say | wolf | I'm Eksmati, Tallinn University's Student Union mascot. I'll help you navigate all the quests. Let's get started!
say | wolf | Use "WASD" or the "Arrow Keys" to follow the path, hold "Shift" to run, and press the "Spacebar" to jump.
